Package PokerProject

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    VideoPoker
    Interface VideoPoker is the structure of Video Poker Game.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Card
    Class Card represents each one of the 52 cards from the Deck.
    Debug
    Class Debug extends Class Game and it represents the Debug Mode of playing Video Poker.
    Deck
    Class Deck represents 52 different cards (as in a real deck).
    Game
    Class Game implements Interface VideoPoker and it represents the core functioning of the Video Poker.
    Interactive
    Class Interactive extends Class Game and it represents the Interactive Mode of playing Video Poker.
    Player
    Class Player represents the player of Video Poker.
    Simulation
    Class Simulation extends Class Game and it represents the Simulation Mode of playing Video Poker.
    Statistics
    Class Statistics is responsible for analyzing the performance of the player in the game.
